者外地二本。人们总盯着 985,211, 总提上海的一本率有多少。殊不知即使在上海，高考考不上本科的人也比考上 985，211 的人多。 现实很残酷的，对于四校八大的学生来说，上海高考很简单，比外地简单多了。但对于有些上海普通高中的学生来说，上海高考其实很难，能考上一本的概率微乎其微。 更可怕的是，家长对孩子的期望还那么高。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-6778214a588e20b131272f252f1a1b94_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/461132796"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I84jlq7ux3KNuEAMaCDY0NzUzNTkzINPorIUGMAE4gwFAH3IJNDYxMTMyNzk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1625540835.1904", "card_id": "Q_469950659", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大家遇到过哪些租房被骗的经历？学生毕业第一次租房如何避免踩雷？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "又到了一年一度的毕业季，很多刚毕业的学生面临毕业后的第一场考试—租房。怎样找到适合自己的房子，怎样租房不被骗，让很多租房小白无所适从。 刚刚踏入社会的毕业生租房需要注意问题呢？你有哪些租房被骗的经历？在租房过程中如何避免踩雷？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8a424e23859488c68511eaaee9dcda49_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469950659"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I84jlq7ux3KNuEAMaCDY2NzEzMjcxIOeQhYcGMAE4dEAgcgk0Njk5NTA2NTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1625540835.190794", "card_id": "Q_462389144", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 136}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "游戏《原神》里最让你心酸的场面是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c86a79e42168afddfd0edc8db348fd6b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/462389144"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I84jlq7ux3KNuEAMaCDY1MDMyNTIyIJGS0oUGMAY49QJAIXIJNDYyMzg5MTQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type"